Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inherited will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tide of the times... People's dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These things cannot be stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as people seek the answer of freedom,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}these things will never cease to be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:42.02,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,mirai dake shinjiteru dareka ga warattemo kamawanai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.52,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,hashitteru jounetsu ga anata o kiramekaseru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:53.53,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,mabushi sugi, demo mitsumete itai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.03,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dokka "bigaku" kanjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.71,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dare ni mo nitenai yume no senaka o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.98,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,oikakete oikaketeku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.27,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,doramatikku te ni ireru made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.33,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dare ni mo mienai yume no katachi o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.39,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,tsukamaete tsukamaeteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:31.40,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,watashi wa tsuite yuku kara atsui kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.49,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,tsujitsuma awase betsu ni iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.84,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,arifureta nichijou yori mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.08,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,paradaisu mezashite hashire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:42.02,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I only believe in the future, I don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.52,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:53.53,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,it's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.03,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.71,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I follow, follow in the footsteps of a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.98,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.27,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.33,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.39,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,of a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:31.40,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go with you, so passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.49,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I don't really need everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.84,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.08,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.48,0:02:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:26.04,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1025,2000)\pos(286,104)}Blue-nosed Reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:26.04,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1025,2000)\pos(423.5,410)}Chopper's Secret
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.38,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,backwards?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.06,0:02:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too slow... and you're \Nnot completely hiding, either...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.44,0:02:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh... Shut up, human!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And, how's your fever?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It talked!!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet, Chopper!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.25,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fever seems to have \Ncome down a little, girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.31,0:03:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,38.2 degrees... Hmm... \NYou're doing more or less all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.06,0:03:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor. Dr. Kureha.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Doctorine.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.57,0:03:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm in the...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My secret to staying young?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't ask that.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.79,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. \NYou're in the castle on top of the mountain.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there were two others besides me, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.96,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're sleeping in the next room...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,very deeply. What tough guys...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the cause.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.73,0:04:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You were bitten by a bug called Kestia.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.77,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a poisonous tick that lives in jungles \Nwith high temperature and humidity.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're bitten by it, bacteria come in and
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.23,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,keep you in pain by lying dormant \Ninside your body for 5 days.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It causes high fever of above 40 degrees,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,coinfection, myocarditis, arteritis, cerebritis!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.54,0:04:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the infection's progression \Nfrom the bitten area,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.12,0:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say you've been infected for three days.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.17,0:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The suffering must've been unusually harsh,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.04,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but it would've eased up in 2 more \Ndays even without any treatment.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In 2 more days...?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.26,0:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because you would've died in 2 days.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the "5-day disease."
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.48,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Kestia died out 100 years ago,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was useful that I kept \Nthe antibiotic just in case.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you guys come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you out walking around \Nwith your belly exposed
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in a jungle on an ancient island or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just silly...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That ring a bell?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What a crazy girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.76,0:05:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.92,0:05:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in bed. \NYour treatment hasn't completely finished yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as my fever comes down, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My body will take care of itself after that, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too optimistic.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.57,0:05:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This disease normally takes \Nat least 10 days to fully treat.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.31,0:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, if you want to \Nsuffer some more and die...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.57,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with my medicine, \Nyou'll have to rest at least 3 days.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay here for 3 days!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to take Vivi to Alabasta soon!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.00,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When a patient of mine leaves me,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,she's either cured or dead. \NI won't let you get away.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He climbed this mountain with his bare hands?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.20,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This 5000m high Drum Rock?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,His entire body is nearly frostbitten.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he thinking dressing like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat water immediately and throw him into it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's bleeding badly.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.60,0:06:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,6 broken ribs and a spinal fissure.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I operate on him?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the most critical one is this girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's dying.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.20,0:07:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper! \NHave phenicol, cardiotonic and tialcillin ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she have an infection?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. \NThe pathogen isn't from this island.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.08,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll make both that \Nbleeding kid and this girl all better.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So rest assured.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're my friends...!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.43,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the picture. I'll save them.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper! Let's begin treatment!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're my friends...!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.65,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.75,0:08:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Venison stew needs to be \Ncooked in a pot for 3 hours...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the meat becomes properly tender...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Venison...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh! Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Luffy! I'll cook this guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.84,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.35,0:08:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You got better?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.26,0:09:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then! I'll make a nutritious \Nvenison dish for Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.11,0:09:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised! \NThey can already move around?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.19,0:09:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that talking stuffed \Ndeer with a blue nose?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You asking me what he is?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away, meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.95,0:09:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Luffy! \NI'm telling you not to eat it yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, humans!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.96,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Chopper. \NHe's just a reindeer with a blue nose.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Reindeers don't speak.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it, you jerks!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's different from ordinary reindeers in some way,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's different...?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.10,0:09:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not food!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just because he ate a Human-Human Fruit. \NThat's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.44,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A Human-Human Fruit... \NOne of the devil fruits...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.03,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a reindeer who gained the humans' abilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.95,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats! Rats!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.62,0:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I taught him everything \NI know about medicine.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.01,0:10:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wapol-{\i1}sama{\i0}. \NThat Straw Hat is up there...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to get a bit hungry.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat the rubber man for a snack.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.82,0:10:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going up.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.54,0:10:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.54,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find him?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.71,0:10:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}! Don't die!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find him in time, for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Be alive, Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there! Help...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta bow.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.68,0:11:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, don't just stand there and help us!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that thing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.82,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We found him!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We found Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! They found him?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no heartbeat.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.35,0:11:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Become one of my crew! \NPlease, old lady!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a doctor on our ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy... You said that's your name, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.73,0:11:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just say "old lady"?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did, old la...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.56,0:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch... what you say!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.95,0:12:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still in the youthful 130s.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.11,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... What an incredible old hag...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.54,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you asking me to be a pirate?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a waste of my glorious time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.18,0:12:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? \NLet's go on an adventure, old lady!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.30,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey. I just told you to \Nwatch what you say, didn't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're pirates...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.60,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.07,0:12:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.57,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,– Wait, meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,– Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, brats!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.74,0:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! \NI'll cook a nutritious reindeer dish!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.67,0:13:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, I'll eat you guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Old hag!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the heck did she come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's coming! She's coming! \NShe's coming! She's coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about the food. \NI just want some peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow...? \NEven though this is inside the castle...?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold...!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I should close the door.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in bed!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have a fever!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't. \NIt seems like it's pretty much gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.81,0:13:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I lost them...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.14,0:13:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Doctorine's medicine works well, \Nthe fever goes away quickly.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kestia's bacteria still remain in your body.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the antibiotic shot \Nand stay in bed, or you'll...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been attending me, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna be thanked by a human!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mock me! You jerk!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, you dummy!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, don't be so...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the type that can't hide their emotions...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.48,0:14:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This castle is strange. \NIt's cold and there's snow inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! It's cold!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I told you before, you're slow!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.58,0:15:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's snow everywhere in the castle.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The doors for the unused \Nrooms are all frozen, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Hold it! Hold it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.53,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, Luffy! \NGive up on asking that old hag to join us!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.08,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not a doctor! \NShe's trying to kill us!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys pirates?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.84,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Real ones?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Real ones.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.51,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a flag with a skull?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's attached to our ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you interested in pirates?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You idiot! No!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.48,0:16:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Then...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.57,0:16:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,wanna come, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To the sea! \NWhy don't you come with us...?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.09,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, that'll help me a lot!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If we have a doctor on our ship,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have to stay here for 3 days, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, on our ship, we...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.83,0:16:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,D... Don't be ridiculous! \NI'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can stay with humans!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.22,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,To start with, don't you get scared when you see me?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.72,0:16:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a reindeer, but I stand on \Ntwo legs and I even speak...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.43,0:16:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you trying to scare me?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My nose is blue, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.86,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Reindeer!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Those brats sure are quick.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it... girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.26,0:17:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.31,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tempting the reindeer without \Nmy permission while I'm not here?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.10,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Do I need permission \Nto make a move on a man?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't. \NIf you wanna take him, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.86,0:17:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't be easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a scar in his heart...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big scar that even I can't cure...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment he was born into this world,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,his group and even his parents abandoned him...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.87,0:17:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because he had a blue nose.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.33,0:17:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He always walked at the very back \Nof the group all by himself...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,even though he was a new-born child...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.80,0:17:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And one day, he ate a devil fruit
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and was treated as a monster even more.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.19,0:18:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The reindeers fiercely pressured him to leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.69,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He was no longer an ordinary reindeer in any way.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, he wanted friends...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.97,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So he went down to a village, \Nas a human this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.67,0:18:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... what's that creature?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.14,0:18:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But his figure wasn't exactly human, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, his nose stayed blue, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.63,0:18:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a yeti!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous! \NGet the children inside quickly!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A gun! Bring me a gun!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.64,0:18:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot him to death!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.68,0:18:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.12,0:19:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't know what was wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.01,0:19:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor did he know what to blame...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.05,0:19:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He just wanted friends, \Nyet he was called a monster...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He was no longer a reindeer...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't a human, either...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.81,0:19:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lived all alone like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.02,0:19:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you guys heal the scar in his heart?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.07,0:19:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy. Look at that door at \Nthe front entrance. It's wide open.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.45,0:19:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder it's cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, let's close this door.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With it open like this, there's no difference \Nbetween outside and inside the castle.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.26,0:20:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop it! Don't touch that door!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.71,0:20:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind what he says. \NLet's close it, or we'll freeze to death.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.85,0:20:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.13,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Didn't I tell you to... stop it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.65,0:20:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with him? Why is he angry?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Luffy. Come over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up there.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.95,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.58,0:20:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're baby snowbirds.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if we close the door, they'll fall...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.93,0:20:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they can't close it...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he speaking earlier?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, come to think of it, I sort of \Nremember him standing on two legs.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's walking on two legs...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a reindeer...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.01,0:21:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fluffy...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.80,0:21:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's short...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He becomes big...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.67,0:21:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's a monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.15,0:21:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cool guy! He's interesting!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.82,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Let's have him join us!
