Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:10.43,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}Even this sleepless town has dozed off for now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:17.02,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}From today forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:22.82,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}something's going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:28.07,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I'm sure I can start fresh,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:33.12,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}since I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:38.25,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}Just by having you by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:43.59,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I feel I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:48.84,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}I wonder how far I can go,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:54.01,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}towards the place that leads to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:23:02.27,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}Off in the distance it shines, encompassing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:06.03,ED5-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}Before dawn
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.20,0:23:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Did you see the reindeer?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you guys! Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.58,0:23:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not that we're not trying to eat him.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.41,0:23:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper has had lots of hardships in his life.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.37,0:23:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.96,0:23:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard that there was \None person who accepted him.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.59,0:23:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What kind of person was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.67,0:23:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.09,0:23:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,An Outcast's Dream! \NHiriluk the Quack!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.26,0:23:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:35.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(275,95)}An Outcast's Dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:35.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(401.5,410)}Hiriluk the Quack!
